Package org.spongepowered.configurate.objectmapping.meta

Annotation Type PostProcess

@Retention(RUNTIME) @Target(METHOD) public @interface PostProcess
Indicate that a method in an object-mappable object is intended for post-processing.

The annotated method will be invoked after all fields in the object have been populated by the object mapper.

The annotated method must be non-static and may only declare a thrown type of SerializationException.

Since:
4.2.0
